            "severity": "中等",
            "subcategory": "應用交付 - 應用閘道",
            "text": "對應用程式登陸區域中的所有公共IP位址使用 DDoS 網路或IP保護計畫。",
            "training": "https://learn.microsoft.com/learn/paths/secure-networking-infrastructure/",
            "waf": "安全"
        },
        {
